      <item>
        <title>Mossflower, a CSS Global Reset</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;Mossflower is a &lt;strong&gt;global reset&lt;/strong&gt; CSS utility for both LESS and SASS.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Both robust and bare-bones; you won’t find yourself fighting against this utility.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;It is &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/herereadthis/mossflower&quot;&gt;available on Github&lt;/a&gt; to use and modify as you please.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;It helps you spin up new web applications faster by &lt;em&gt;reducing boilderplate CSS&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;!--more--&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;build&quot;&gt;Build&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;html&quot;&gt;$ git clone https://github.com/herereadthis/mossflower.git
$ cd mossflower/
$ npm install
$ grunt&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;setup&quot;&gt;Setup&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The Bellmaker assumes you have basic terminal skills and knowledge of Git. Additionally, you should be using Grunt.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;css-importing&quot;&gt;CSS importing&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;recommended-add-the-bellmaker-as-a-bower-dependency&quot;&gt;Recommended: Add the Bellmaker as a Bower dependency&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;html&quot;&gt;$ bower install --save mossflower&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;alternative-add-mossflower-as-a-submodule&quot;&gt;Alternative: Add Mossflower as a submodule&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;html&quot;&gt;$ cd my_repo
$ git submodule add https://github.com/herereadthis/mossflower.git
$ git add mossflower .gitmodules
$ git commit -m &amp;quot;adds Mossflower submodule&amp;quot;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&quot;as-less-add-to-your-imports&quot;&gt;As LESS: Add to your imports&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;css&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;@import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;/PATH_TO/../mossflower/src/less/main.less&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://badge.fury.io/bo/mossflower&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://badge.fury.io/bo/mossflower.svg&quot; alt=&quot;Bower version&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
